latestPosts.caption:
Send this to someone who needs to hear it.

Your skin doesn’t need perfection.
it needs patience, consistency, and a little kindness especially on the days you feel like it’s betraying you.

These reminders are for anyone who’s ever felt ashamed of their acne, scars, texture, or pigmentation. you are not alone and your worth was never skin-deep.

If you’re into Pan Asian, this one’s a hidden gem worth bookmarking.

Struggling with a damaged skin barrier? I’ve been there, and trust me, the right moisturiser makes all the difference! Here are my top 3 picks that have personally helped me heal, soothe, and strengthen my skin over the years: 

Olivarrier Comfort Barrier Cream– A deeply nourishing Korean gem that locks in hydration and restores your barrier without feeling heavy. My go-to for when my skin is extra sensitive! (use code LASHITA on skinbae website to save some 💰)

Let’s Resolve Bear Hug Moisturiser– Just like a warm hug for your skin! Super lightweight yet hydrating, with bamboo water to calm irritation and keep your barrier happy. I have finished one bottle & I’m currently using the 2nd one!)

PureAm Authentic Barrier Cream Balm – A repair powerhouse with vegan ceramides and organic glycerin—perfect for when my skin is feeling dry, damaged, or just needs extra love. (use code LASHITA on skinbae website to save some 💰)

If your skin barrier is crying out for help, these might be your new best friends! Have you tried any of these?
